  "text": "A prospect of the researches that we would like to deepen in future work is to determine the financial characteristics that each of the languages and models is able to describe in order to define a profitable business process. We are now discussing whether the chance discovery process [CITATION_1] can be applied to the verification from the financial and business administration viewpoint.",
